00:35:00,180 --> 00:35:01,260
It's just a graze.

863
00:35:06,420 --> 00:35:07,550
Where's your wound?

864
00:35:08,300 --> 00:35:08,860
Wound?

865
00:35:09,140 --> 00:35:09,980
What wound?

866
00:35:10,060 --> 00:35:11,460
Didn't you hurt your hand?

867
00:35:11,460 --> 00:35:12,900
There's blood on your sleeve.

868
00:35:12,900 --> 00:35:13,300
Fine.

869
00:35:13,580 --> 00:35:15,570
Let me make Ji Shu give up on Xining first.

870
00:35:15,570 --> 00:35:17,100
Blood. Blood…

871
00:35:18,180 --> 00:35:18,660
Hey!

872
00:35:18,660 --> 00:35:19,780
You're out of line.

873
00:35:20,580 --> 00:35:21,980
Mr. Ji, I feel dizzy.

874
00:35:22,700 --> 00:35:24,100
Did you get a concussion?

875
00:35:24,220 --> 00:35:26,050
Do you feel any other discomfort?

876
00:35:26,050 --> 00:35:26,690
Yes.

877
00:35:26,690 --> 00:35:29,660
I feel tightness in my chest.

878
00:35:30,620 --> 00:35:32,480
Drop the act or I'll dock your pay.

879
00:35:33,500 --> 00:35:35,860
Mr. Ji, how can you think I'm acting?

880
00:35:37,340 --> 00:35:38,620
I'm in so much pain now.

881
00:35:38,860 --> 00:35:40,190
Then go to the hospital.

882
00:35:41,940 --> 00:35:42,580
Hospital?

883
00:35:43,220 --> 00:35:43,740
No, I…

884
00:35:43,940 --> 00:35:44,860
Go see a doctor.

885
00:35:45,100 --> 00:35:47,100
You don't want to get too ill and die.

886
00:35:48,940 --> 00:35:49,620
Mr. Ji,

887
00:35:50,300 --> 00:35:51,820
thank you for being so considerate.

888
00:35:51,820 --> 00:35:52,300
Well,

889
00:35:52,860 --> 00:35:54,720
could you send me to the hospital?

890
00:35:55,700 --> 00:35:56,820
What do you think?

891
00:35:56,900 --> 00:35:57,500
Mr. Ji,

892
00:35:57,860 --> 00:35:59,250
if I'm going to die soon,

893
00:35:59,700 --> 00:36:01,300
I hope you're the last person

894
00:36:01,500 --> 00:36:02,500
I see before I die.

895
00:36:04,260 --> 00:36:05,020
Xining.

896
00:36:05,900 --> 00:36:06,660
Don't get the wrong idea.

897
00:36:06,660 --> 00:36:08,660
There's nothing between me and her.

898
00:36:08,690 --> 00:36:09,180
Mr. Ji,

899
00:36:09,300 --> 00:36:11,140
let's send her to the hospital together.

900
00:36:11,140 --> 00:36:11,900
No.

901
00:36:15,180 --> 00:36:15,780
Xining.

902
00:36:16,460 --> 00:36:16,890
Well,

903
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:19,180
I've liked Mr. Ji for a long time.

904
00:36:19,180 --> 00:36:19,580
You…

905
00:36:19,580 --> 00:36:21,140
I want to be alone with him.

906
00:36:22,580 --> 00:36:24,060
You like Mr. Ji?

907
00:36:24,940 --> 00:36:25,780
Qi.

908
00:36:26,460 --> 00:36:29,180
You like Mr. Ji?

909
00:36:32,380 --> 00:36:34,460
Xining, I didn't know her before today.

910
00:36:34,460 --> 00:36:35,340
Trust me.

911
00:36:36,300 --> 00:36:37,020
Let go!

912
00:36:38,060 --> 00:36:38,730
Mr. Ji.

913
00:36:39,500 --> 00:36:40,980
I know you didn't know me

914
00:36:41,340 --> 00:36:42,540
and you won't like me,

915
00:36:43,130 --> 00:36:45,540
but I've loved you for ten years.

916
00:36:45,900 --> 00:36:46,460
Qi.

917
00:36:46,490 --> 00:36:48,290
Have you ever thought about why?

918
00:36:48,700 --> 00:36:49,560
-If... -Let go!

919
00:36:49,650 --> 00:36:51,460
If I don't have much time left,

920
00:36:51,820 --> 00:36:53,780
I hope you can be the one by my side.

921
00:36:54,500 --> 00:36:55,820
I don't have time

922
00:36:56,260 --> 00:36:57,660
for this farce.

923
00:36:57,740 --> 00:36:58,460
Let go.

924
00:37:06,540 --> 00:37:07,780
You're vomiting blood!

925
00:37:07,780 --> 00:37:09,420
Send her to the hospital, Mr. Ji.

926
00:37:09,420 --> 00:37:10,620
You can't let her die.

927
00:37:14,780 --> 00:37:15,460
Fine.

928
00:37:25,060 --> 00:37:26,780
Most people keep their feelings inside.

929
00:37:26,780 --> 00:37:28,490
Qi is so brave.

930
00:37:29,300 --> 00:37:30,980
I hope all unrequited love

931
00:37:31,420 --> 00:37:33,020
could have a happy ending.

932
00:37:34,570 --> 00:37:35,780
I'm not going to the hospital.

933
00:37:35,780 --> 00:37:37,500
I won't faint again, Mr. Ji.

934
00:37:38,570 --> 00:37:39,210
It hurts.

935
00:38:02,460 --> 00:38:03,900
I'll send you to go to the hospital.

936
00:38:03,900 --> 00:38:05,960
Maybe you need an operation in the ER.

937
00:38:07,860 --> 00:38:08,300
Here.

938
00:38:09,980 --> 00:38:11,330
The cost

939
00:38:11,530 --> 00:38:13,740
of putting up this show is too high.

940
00:38:22,340 --> 00:38:22,860
Ji…

941
00:38:34,820 --> 00:38:36,060
After some rest,

942
00:38:36,380 --> 00:38:37,640
I feel much better now.

943
00:38:38,780 --> 00:38:39,260
Mr. Ji,

944
00:38:39,660 --> 00:38:41,820
please pull over.

945
00:38:41,860 --> 00:38:43,180
I don't need to go to the hospital.

946
00:38:43,180 --> 00:38:43,940
Don't worry.

947
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:46,500
I won't give up the life of any employee.

948
00:38:46,980 --> 00:38:48,840
Even if God wants you to die today,

949
00:38:49,060 --> 00:38:50,990
I'll make you live to see tomorrow.

950
00:38:52,140 --> 00:38:54,060
It's not that serious.

951
00:38:54,820 --> 00:38:55,850
It's not up to you.

952
00:38:56,140 --> 00:38:57,940
The doctor has the final say.

953
00:39:08,900 --> 00:39:10,300
Why are you looking at me?

954
00:39:10,660 --> 00:39:11,460
Mr. Ji,

955
00:39:11,500 --> 00:39:12,860
maybe

956
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:14,910
you don't like the way I look at you,

957
00:39:15,620 --> 00:39:17,460
but you can see in my eyes

958
00:39:17,820 --> 00:39:19,220
that I'm really into you.

959
00:39:20,340 --> 00:39:21,140
I feel so hot.

960
00:39:23,780 --> 00:39:24,540
Qi,

961
00:39:25,620 --> 00:39:27,700
as the boss of such a big entertainment company,

962
00:39:27,700 --> 00:39:29,540
I've seen countless women who are hotter than you.

963
00:39:29,540 --> 00:39:30,420
Do you think

964
00:39:30,620 --> 00:39:32,170
I'd be interested in you?

965
00:39:34,780 --> 00:39:35,500
I'm just

966
00:39:36,340 --> 00:39:37,010
having a fever.

967
00:39:37,010 --> 00:39:37,580
I…

968
00:39:40,900 --> 00:39:41,980
I want to throw up.

969
00:39:43,780 --> 00:39:44,980
Pull over.
